    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Slate primarily used for general building purposes; such slate should be free from pits, cracks, or others defects that could affect its durability or strength.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
